{"tid":131974,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"講吓你準備DSE嗰陣遇過嘅困難/負擔","createTime":"2017-02-23T12:49:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T17:18:37.000Z","uid":37971,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f57eb049e9c68fe7e919e48582c93e0bc6a2166f","tid":131974,"uid":37971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T12:49:09.000Z","msg":"例如話你遇到啲咩心理壓力<br />\n或者點樣影響你嘅日常生活等等<br />\n總之有關準備DSE(或者已畢業嘅巴絲以前準備會考)對你造成嘅壞影響都可以講吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小弟咁啱做緊有關嘅research <br />\n順便開個post比大家呻吓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw祝今屆DSE嘅巴絲成功入到大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40def039515ce696b4bec8147a5afceccce35a08","tid":131974,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T13:00:25.000Z","msg":"未考已經知日文得B<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3790fcff61d6bcbbfd8618eb8b0a8acca95c7593","tid":131974,"uid":13835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T13:03:23.000Z","msg":"無<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗住全科合格之後asso算<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"744cae4b92ebdc5f18d41abc080da4b537b1c080","tid":131974,"uid":31040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T13:03:30.000Z","msg":"成日諗遲啲先溫 點知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a83ec9f0afc24495c17cdc8dd0011b8ea65d8304","tid":131974,"uid":66252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T13:07:17.000Z","msg":"好撚緊張啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n尤其我父母話到明我入唔到大學就唔會再理我<br />\n我真係無後路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces