 點知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當年我嘅form 4都係咁<br />\n結果我讀咗3年先，依家升到form 5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家晚晚溫到10點11點後先返歸食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18a84c2dd4b292863f5ac025cc93e84373295c68","tid":131974,"uid":37971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T13:15:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好撚緊張啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n尤其我父母話到明我入唔到大學就唔會再理我<br />\n我真係無後路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n平時成績點樣？中上？中下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f1663004410ed5def66758ac4abc296e4827851","tid":131974,"uid":60916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T13:16:48.000Z","msg":"一份一份既past paper打擊自己既信心<br />\n特別係中英<br />\n最後越讀越頹 最後得18分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa0e53de980b42852f2e9b0c9e600673399da78","tid":131974,"uid":83941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T13:18:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0f3b73a0c3422c97b8bd7d0f467541905ad3cda0","tid":131974,"uid":37971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T13:20:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>阿爸cancer擴散 feel到佢身體差咗 阿媽全程返唔到香港</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得返你照顧佢？<br />\n屋企人要緊，DSE如果冇時間溫而衰咗嘅，可以再考過<br />\n希望你啊爸最後冇事"},{"pid":"a2cc301ab11f8e6fc42195495355549d82409dcc","tid":131974,"uid":3120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T15:43:29.000Z","msg":"阿爺過世同埋考完mock開始厭戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33df97c8a6305e465420b6db8149939b979e9040","tid":131974,"uid":3120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T15:44:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>阿爺過世同埋考完mock開始厭戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\npredict 20 最後得18<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dd26019f001cb17f22a121922307adf8c7a1309","tid":131974,"uid":21501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T15:44:18.000Z","msg":"疊音事件受害者<br />\n以為自己Paper5 U<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ccc2ece5d1d4172570c332528284d713435b1e0","tid":131974,"uid":21501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T15:44:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>疊音事件受害者<br />\n以為自己Paper5 U<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來講準備，自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acc811de5130de854f5f854d52098aa1271d92e6","tid":131974,"uid":60733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T15:44:50.000Z","msg":"電腦係面前"},{"pid":"7403ed6863141bdea19d7d558925ff000086db64","tid":131974,"uid":35080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T15:45:10.000Z","msg":"唔知點進步<br />\n唔知點做數學m2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />先穩有星"},{"pid":"1399675eca1f8d33bc5a02c604c21f8fcd7cc5ad","tid":131974,"uid":63697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T17:32:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>疊音事件受害者<br />\n以為自己Paper5 U<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來講準備，自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最後lv幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac82e405b7c773bcd57c5dab0ec31a1cb89e84e2","tid":131974,"uid":19647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T17:44:12.000Z","msg":"感情問題 真係好困擾"},{"pid":"c9987e0eced6c525b4dbd73feb0ee473d2f16612","tid":131974,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T20:02:00.000Z","msg":"除了第一次外，第二和第三次自己定力不足，所以全都失敗收場<br />\n<br />\n還記得retake考中文聆聽卷時收音機出現故障，需轉至特別室應考，結果聆聽卷只拿到2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"019f943a326589e87452fe3ea1cf9d92f9943a72","tid":131974,"uid":83915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T00:54:55.000Z","msg":"考試前一個月阿爸阿媽離婚 抑鬱症覆發<br />\n最後比預期考差咗5分 入大學邊緣 <br />\n雖然最後有無咁好既大學offer<br />\n而家阿爸想補償我，比咗機會我去外國<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"410f371643794ea1feb437621ebd32a6a2753f63","tid":131974,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T01:08:14.000Z","msg":"課程考小心多過識幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到成日背marking<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdf1e0bf3a7c60b75fc606b58d7878174c824fc6","tid":131974,"uid":40820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T13:36:15.000Z","msg":"覺得人生冇意義唔想溫書<br />\n但又有個考試係到，搞到打機或者hea99都有罪惡感<br />\n雖然都係冇乜點溫"},{"pid":"90f5e58d3286ea4904188aeea09c32bb75e56490","tid":131974,"uid":69090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T15:49:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2abf12cc6437027c370d2031d5c5c565bab4ab08","tid":131974,"uid":73317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T16:50:38.000Z","msg":"迫自己迫得好緊<br />\n頭痛藥送咖啡 無限loop <br />\n壓力大到試過訓2個鐘醒一次 持續2個禮拜<br />\n手指痛到眼淚都湧出黎<br />\n最大既遺憾 係DSE中識到曾經的女朋友 但係自己果時應試時悲觀自卑令到最後把握唔到機會<br />\n人地睇我會覺得我好勁 好勤力<br />\n最後入到大學 好似好風光 但又有幾多人知堅持的代價同心酸"},{"pid":"845cae2294b1caa3f0e1d6a8e7657cd27b0aaca6","tid":131974,"uid":12873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T17:06:20.000Z","msg":"2016 DSE：同上面有位巴打一樣 又係考試前有屋企人離世 其實嗰個屋企人係聖誕節已經入咗院 但去到2月尾終於捱唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我3月10號考oral 3月8號佢先出殯完 我去考嗰陣其實個mood都未調節好 但都要頂硬上既啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  結果中文就衰咗今年要考多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （本身自己又廢）<br />\n不過兩年都係咁 臨考果陣成日覺得好似未溫哂咁/溫漏咗少少野 搞到好鬼緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實唔洗咁驚既 呢d真係聽天由命 如果你真係溫得熟 你考試嗰陣遲早會諗返起 （溫唔熟就另計啦）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ced11c00314a3fb7a0c6ea1bde0123884200237","tid":131974,"uid":30250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T17:06:59.000Z","msg":"迫得自己好緊+1<br />\n對中文科好有期望 份份卷都穩陣係爭oral唔多得<br />\n去完補習社啲oral practice俾兩個examiner批評左幾句 即刻內心崩潰 喺條街到一路行一路唔受控咁喊<br />\n喊左幾個鐘  覺得自己點解咁冇用 f4果陣已經係level4 點解黎到最後一個月仲係level4 練極都冇進步 內心真係好崩潰<br />\n之後果晚返到屋企仲要收到補習個中文mock寄返返黎<br />\n個分好唔理想 成個人負能量到一個點<br />\n<br />\n利申從來唔會因為成績而喊 真係壓力使然"},{"pid":"104ecdc29328a2e0849c52850d609062877e6d9d","tid":131974,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T17:15:14.000Z","msg":"中文科付出好多努力都答唔到八成，即使問老師都答我唔到，只係得過且過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff36a4e0dca615639ce7485c0b7ce729be8c272f","tid":131974,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T17:17:24.000Z","msg":"我到大學都諗唔到中文點樣有8成 9成分<br />\n如果得唔到，個分存在有咩意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有可能，應該要點做??"},{"pid":"a54944c29c881a9d0dd14681e443ee9c2d3b3df0","tid":131974,"uid":30250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T17:22:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我到大學都諗唔到中文點樣有8成 9成分<br />\n如果得唔到，個分存在有咩意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有可能，應該要點做??</blockquote><br />\n好似係有人真係拎到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過係講緊寫作/綜合"},{"pid":"0b27997309e9633acc10456f2f3349250ce277c9","tid":131974,"uid":2896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T14:57:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>課程考小心多過識幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到成日背marking<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAgree <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73e84039354995f685fcb2960ea76cfba41cfc9a","tid":131974,"uid":17306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T15:06:20.000Z","msg":"就黎考dse條女都成撚日搵我嘈交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"855edfac36d6bb8b68d00a4ea85b2de1bd27a903","tid":131974,"uid":82602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T15:22:14.000Z","msg":"study leave每日8點起身去自修室6點番屋企<br />\n4月就溫到10點左右 自己本身想數好啲<br />\n日日操數 操到頭痛 係咁啪必理痛 <br />\n本身都窮 加上平時老母以為我唔洗番學就冇比飯錢我 所以我果個月餐餐都食包...<br />\n本身講野唔叻 啲老師仲話我得3 比盡4 所以考前果日我緊張到爆喊 精神壓力爆登。。 <br />\n總之就好辛苦 好難先捱過依段日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa78fc96fee23ed6ab0cec03d8b34832d45d2d83","tid":131974,"uid":17306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T15:27:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>study leave每日8點起身去自修室6點番屋企<br />\n4月就溫到10點左右 自己本身想數好啲<br />\n日日操數 操到頭痛 係咁啪必理痛 <br />\n本身都窮 加上平時老母以為我唔洗番學就冇比飯錢我 所以我果個月餐餐都食包...<br />\n本身講野唔叻 啲老師仲話我得3 比盡4 所以考前果日我緊張到爆喊 精神壓力爆登。。 <br />\n總之就好辛苦 好難先捱過依段日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最後成績點？"},{"pid":"61b2ae1ed72e50d71f4e545ecb4c51d3b7a3f8ca","tid":131974,"uid":82602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T04:50:11.000Z","msg":"<bl